Show HN: Ping your sitemap file and let Google know about your new content
text:
Google only crawls the sitemap when submitted so ping after you add new content is a important.

Recently google release an api to ping so,

I made a ui just 1. Enter the sitemap url and 2. Click the button to Ping your sitemap to Google

title: K-POP Supergroup BTS, worldwide free streaming – Akamai are you OK?
text:
It was rumored that >10M viewers globally will tune in to watch K-POP supergroup BTS FREE Live concert.

The show is running now, and it's barely working from Singapore.

Akamai guys, are you OK? Anyone's child watching the show too?
